{"type": "article", "id": 9558, "title": "H&M 美妆线 H&M Beauty", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-14T07:13:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 18, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235507Yz5C8jckt2rhVNDQ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t最近 H&amp;M 要把他们进军美妆界的计划实现了，他们最近宣布，即将出现的美妆线 H&amp;M Beauty 系列，将会推出 700 多件美妆产品。按照目前 H&amp;M 平民化的快时尚路线，我们似乎也可以期待一下他们会在美妆领域的表现。据了解，H&amp;M Beauty 系列产品将于今年 9 月和大家见面，在线上商店和全世界门店进行销售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235504WFDVBu1ljZUI9n0r.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235505qZtnVEbDd317GJpS.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235505C4HhV9NnXriZJetD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235506prbnzisTf9cBSHoU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235506IiCAsoyGQjuvOFZc.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66608696\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}